reut2-010.sgm,  E. GERMAN EQUIPPED TEXTILE MILL OPENED IN CUBA, A textile mill with an annual productioncapacity of 52 mln square metres of knitted fabric has beenopened officially near Havana, Granma, the official Cubannewspaper, said.    The mill, inaugurated yesterday, is equipped with looms andother machinery from East Germany. A single production line, inoperation since last year, has already produced over seven mlnsquare metres of fabric.    President Fidel Castro and vice-president Carlos RafaelRodriguez were present at the ceremony. Reuter&#3;
