reut2-010.sgm, NEW ZEALAND TREASURY BILL TENDER CANCELLED, New Zealand's Reserve Bank said ithas cancelled the regular weekly Treasury bill tender scheduledfor tomorrow.    The bank said in a statement that it forecasts a small netcash injection into the system over the settlement week.    However, it said it will conduct open market operationsduring the week. After these the cash balance should fluctuatearound 30 mln N.Z. Dlrs. REUTER&#3;
