reut2-010.sgm, SAGE ANALYTICS &lt;SAII> SETS STOCK SPLIT, Sage Analytics International Incsaid its board has declared a three-for-two stock split,payable June 22 to holders of record on June Eight.    The company also said it will redeem warrants tilloutstanding on June Two at 10 cts each.  Each two warrantsallow the purchase of one common share at six dlrs through JuneOne.  There are presently 800,000 warrants outstanding. Reuter&#3;
reut2-010.sgm, U.S. BUDGET DIRECTOR SAYS NO TAX RISE COMPROMISE, Budget director James Miller saidPresident Reagan will not compromise on his vow not to raisetaxes despite pressure from Congress.    No

