reut2-010.sgm, YORK INTERNATIONAL &lt;YRK> TO MAKE ACQUISITIONS, York International Corp said it hasagreed to acquire Frick Co and Frigid Coil/Frick Inc forundisclosed terms.    The company said Frick makes refrigeration equipment andcompressors and Frigid Coil also makes refrigeration equipment. Together the two had revenues of about 50 mln dlrs in 1986.    The company said it hopes to complete the acquisition inMay, subject to its review of Frick and Frigid and regulatoryapprovals. Reuter&#3;
